{"tid":2140746,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：將盡快與深圳商討方便跨境生學習","createTime":"2020-08-05T07:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:20:47.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0e722219817274ffeae03c6d00ea5c86eb138157","tid":2140746,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKdBUfZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKdBUfZ.jpg&h=6cc8de62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄表示，有關小五呈分試方面，不少學校已按當局原先安排提交成績，部分學生因屬跨境學童，暑假前未能進行評估，學校原定希望9月做評估，未來安排有待商討。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄說，本港疫情在變化，開學安排亦有變，當局正在內部考慮不同方案，會盡快開始與深圳方面商討，研究有沒有更多選擇可方便跨境生在深圳學習。<br />\n<br />\n至於中學文憑試方面，楊潤雄說考評局減少了校本評核的工作量，但按照疫情發展，當局會要求考評局多作預案，例如在學生有更長時間不能回校的情況下，考試時間表能否作適當調節等。"},{"pid":"6b3c0bc483e6f6d5e9ad579ba9ad7a137ff07eb1","tid":2140746,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"深圳：on9"},{"pid":"af3326c6463434c9ab5b70a9001c90679e4d3959","tid":2140746,"uid":98139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"仔女幾時同深圳人做同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9644926d8f056ec8cf9cfec088ab4fb2538798","tid":2140746,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"叫佢地直接讀深圳既學校咪最方便囉，住邊度就喺返邊度讀書，天經地義合情合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4db8d5fedbe9c7e06b3401709df895e7fe5f79","tid":2140746,"uid":293543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"而家深圳仲驚過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78ba53a8bd05352161b6ca192dcc74453934502","tid":2140746,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"送哂d教畜上去囉"},{"pid":"b8c2feab8a59fd6f4